A potential safespot for ranged/magic combat.

The profit rate assumes 200 kills per hour. Your actual profits may be higher or lower depending on your speed and luck.

Hobgoblins can be found in the Edgeville Dungeon (north of the hill giants) and on the peninsula west of the Crafting Guild. They primarily drop limpwurt roots, but have a few rune and gem drops that are worth picking up. After filling up an inventory with loot, players can use a brass key as a shortcut to bank at the Grand Exchange.

Due to constantly changing prices on the Grand Exchange, some information in this article may or may not be current.
It is strongly recommended to check the live prices on the Grand Exchange before making large investments in any method.
All prices on this page are cached, meaning it is possible that they appear out of date.
